ABOUT:

This recommendation system algorithm implements:
- Two-tower retrieval architecture for efficient candidate selection
- Transformer-based ranking with candidate isolation
- Multi-action engagement prediction
- Hash-based embeddings for scalability
- Real-time content ingestion and filtering

Created by Mohammad Faiz as a personal project, now shared with the community.

